#: ../../../dev/index.rst:238
msgid "spin docs"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../dev/index.rst:240
msgid ""
"You can also run ``make`` from the ``doc`` directory. ``make help`` lists "
"all targets."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../dev/index.rst:243
msgid ""
"To get the appropriate dependencies and other requirements, see :ref:`howto-"
"build-docs`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../dev/index.rst:247
msgid "Fixing Warnings"
msgstr ""

